snippet.textDisplay:
I've always loved this song, it's been sung by many a legend - superbly. That said, this rendition, with its combination of Surayya Khanuns haunting voice and Anwar Maqsood's spellbinding recitation doesn't make one cry as much as it rips your heart out if your chest! Head and shoulders above the rest. Emotion so strong that anyone's heart would melt. 

MashAllah. This will take some beating.
